Maintainer: Domingos Cardoso <domingoscardoso@jbrj.gov.br>
Description: Provides tools to access and analyze plant specimen records from
    REFLORA Virtual Herbarium, a botanical data repository maintained by the
    Rio de Janeiro Botanical Garden. Users can retrieve, filter, and summarize
    specimen data using taxonomic, geographic, or temporal criteria. The
    package supports downloading structured Darwin Core (DwC-A) archives and
    integrates with tidyverse workflows for downstream analysis and visualization.
